==Irish==

===Pronunciation===
{{IPA|[lʲe]}}
===Preposition===
'''le''' (adds '''h''' to vowels)
#[[with]]
====Forms====
Form used before [[definite article]]: [[leis]], as ''leis an [[buachaill|mbuachaill]]'' "with the boy", ''leis na [[cailín|cailíní]] "with the girls"

Inflected forms:
*[[First person|1]][[singular|sg.]] '''[[liom]]''' — [[with]] [[me]]
*[[Second person|2]][[singular|sg.]] '''[[leat]]''' — [[with]] [[you]] ([[singular|sg.]])
*[[Third person|3]][[singular|sg.]][[masculine|m.]] '''[[leis]]''' — [[with]] [[him]], [[with]] [[it]]
*[[Third person|3]][[singular|sg.]][[feminine|f.]] '''[[léi]]''' — [[with]] [[her]], [[with]] [[it]]
*[[First person|1]][[plural|pl.]] '''[[linn]]''' — [[with]] [[us]]
*[[Second person|2]][[plural|pl.]] '''[[libh]]''' — [[with]] [[you]] ([[plural|pl.]])
*[[Third person|3]][[plural|pl.]][[masculine|m.]] '''[[leo]]''' — [[with]] [[them]]

